4389026Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate static bool GetResponse(NetworkStream stream, out string response)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    byte[] readBuffer = new byte[32];Di2015NewLine    var asyncReader = stream.BeginRead(readBuffer, 0, readBuffer.Length, null, null);Di2015NewLine    WaitHandle handle = asyncReader.AsyncWaitHandle;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Give the reader 2seconds to respond with a valueDi2015NewLine    bool completed = handle.WaitOne(2000, false);Di2015NewLine    if (completed)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int bytesRead = stream.EndRead(asyncReader);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        StringBuilder message = new StringBuilder();Di2015NewLine        message.Append(Encoding.ASCII.GetString(readBuffer, 0, bytesRead));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (bytesRead == readBuffer.Length)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            // There's possibly more than 32 bytes to read, so get the next Di2015NewLine            // section of the responseDi2015NewLine            string continuedResponse;Di2015NewLine            if (GetResponse(stream, out continuedResponse))Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                message.Append(continuedResponse);Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        response = message.ToString();Di2015NewLine        return true;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    elseDi2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int bytesRead = stream.EndRead(asyncReader);Di2015NewLine        if (bytesRead == 0)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            // 0 bytes were returned, so the read has finishedDi2015NewLine            response = string.Empty;Di2015NewLine            return true;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        elseDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            throw new TimeoutException(Di2015NewLine                "The device failed to read in an appropriate amount of time.");Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4390308Di2015UniqueSeparatorclass StringNumberComparer : IComparer<string>Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    public int Compare(string x, string y)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int compareResult;Di2015NewLine        int xIndex = 0, yIndex = 0;Di2015NewLine        int xIndexLast = 0, yIndexLast = 0;Di2015NewLine        int xNumber, yNumber;Di2015NewLine        int xLength = x.Length;Di2015NewLine        int yLength = y.Length;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        doDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            bool xHasNextNumber = TryGetNextNumber(x, ref xIndex, out xNumber);Di2015NewLine            bool yHasNextNumber = TryGetNextNumber(y, ref yIndex, out yNumber);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            if (!(xHasNextNumber && yHasNextNumber))Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                // At least one the strings has either no more number or contains non-numeric charsDi2015NewLine                // In this case do a string comparison of that last partDi2015NewLine                return x.Substring(xIndexLast).CompareTo(y.Substring(yIndexLast));Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            xIndexLast = xIndex;Di2015NewLine            yIndexLast = yIndex;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            compareResult = xNumber.CompareTo(yNumber);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        while (compareResult == 0Di2015NewLine            && xIndex < xLengthDi2015NewLine            && yIndex < yLength);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return compareResult;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private bool TryGetNextNumber(string text, ref int startIndex, out int number)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        number = 0;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        int pos = text.IndexOf('.', startIndex);Di2015NewLine        if (pos < 0) pos = text.Length;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (!int.TryParse(text.Substring(startIndex, pos - startIndex), out number))Di2015NewLine            return false;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        startIndex = pos + 1;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return true;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4391828Di2015UniqueSeparatorstatic bool CalcBiggestRationalFraction(float target_real, float epsilon, Di2015NewLine    int numerator_max, int denominator_max, Di2015NewLine    out int numerator, out int denominator)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    if((int)Math.Round(target_real * denominator_max) > numerator_max)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        // We were given values that don't match up.Di2015NewLine        // For example, target real = 0.5, but max_num / max_den = 0.3Di2015NewLine        denominator_max = (int)(numerator_max / target_real);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    float bestEpsilon = float.MAX_VALUE;Di2015NewLine    for(int den = denominator_max; den >= denominator_max/2, den--)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int num = (int)Math.Round(target_real * den);Di2015NewLine        float thisEpsilon = Math.abs(((float)num / den) - target_real);Di2015NewLine        if(thisEpsilon < bestEpsilon)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            numerator = num;Di2015NewLine            denominator = den;Di2015NewLine            bestEpsilon = thisEpsilon;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return bestEpsilon < epsilon;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4394017Di2015UniqueSeparatorSwap<T>(T, T)
4394017Di2015UniqueSeparator/* Di2015NewLine * The ref keywords mean "pass by reference" i.e. modify the variables as theyDi2015NewLine * were passed into the method.Di2015NewLine *Di2015NewLine * The <T> in the signature tells the compiler that T is a generic type, in caseDi2015NewLine * the class itself doesn't already declare T a generic type.Di2015NewLine */Di2015NewLinepublic void Swap<T>(ref T x, ref T y)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    // Tells the compiler that temp should be of the same type as x and y,Di2015NewLine    // regardless of what type T may beDi2015NewLine    T temp = x;Di2015NewLine    x = y;Di2015NewLine    y = temp;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineint x = 3, y = 6;Di2015NewLineSwap<int>(ref x, ref y);Di2015NewLineConsole.WriteLine(x + " " + y);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinechar a = 'a', b = 'b';Di2015NewLineSwap<char>(ref a, ref b);Di2015NewLineConsole.WriteLine(a + " " + b);Di2015NewLine

 public static double GetDistanceBetweenPoints(Point p, Point q)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var a = p.X - q.X;Di2015NewLine        var b = p.Y - q.Y;Di2015NewLine        return Math.Sqrt(a * a + b * b);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private static double CalculateTheta(Point p1, Point p2)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var deltaX = Math.Abs(p1.Y - }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public void RotateAndSaveImage(string sourceFile, List<Point> subCoords)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var bitmap = new BitmapImage();Di2015NewLine p2);Di2015NewLine        var height = GetDistanceBetweenPoints(p1, p4);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var transformGroup = new TransformGroup();Di2015NewLine        var rotateTransform = new RotateTransform(theta)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            CenterX = p1.X,Di2015NewLine            CenterY = p1.YDi2015NewLine        };Di2015NewLine        transformGroup.Children.Add(rotateTransform);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var translateTransform = new TranslateTransformDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            X = -p1.X,Di2015NewLine            Y = -p1.YDi2015NewLine        };Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        transformGroup.Children.Add(translateTransform);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var vis = new cont.DrawImage(bitmap, new Rect(Di2015NewLine                new Size(bitmap.PixelWidth, bitmap.PixelHeight)));Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var rtb = new "cat".Anagrams();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            foreach (var anagram in res)Di2015NewLine                Console.WriteLine(anagram.MergeToStr());Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        static IEnumerable<IEnumerable<T>> Anagrams<T>(this IEnumerable<T> collection) where T: IComparable<T>Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            var total = collection.Count();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            // provided str "cat" get all subsets c, a, ca, at, etc (really nonefficient)Di2015NewLine            var subsets = collection.Permutations()Di2015NewLine                .SelectMany(c => Enumerable.Range(1, total).Select(i => c.Take(i)))Di2015NewLine                .Distinct(new CollectionComparer<T>());Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            return subsets;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        public static IEnumerable<IEnumerable<T>> Permutations<T>(this IEnumerable<T> collection)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            return collection.Count() > 1 Di2015NewLine                ?Di2015NewLine                    from ch in collectionDi2015NewLine                    let set = new[] { ch }Di2015NewLine                    from permutation in collection.Except(set).Permutations()Di2015NewLine                    select set.Union(permutation)Di2015NewLine                :Di2015NewLine                    new[] { collection };Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        public static string MergeToStr(this IEnumerable<char> chars)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            return new string(chars.ToArray());Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    }// classDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // cause Distinct implementation is shitDi2015NewLine    public class CollectionComparer<T> : IEqualityComparer<IEnumerable<T>> where T: IComparable<T>Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        Dictionary<IEnumerable<T>, int> dict = new Dictionary<IEnumerable<T>, int>();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        public bool Equals(IEnumerable<T> x, IEnumerable<T> y)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if (x.Count() != y.Count())Di2015NewLine                return false;Di2015NewLine            return x.Zip(y, (xi, yi) => xi.Equals(yi)).All(compareResult => compareResult);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        public int GetHashCode(IEnumerable<T> obj)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            var inDict = dict.Keys.FirstOrDefault(k => Equals(k, obj));Di2015NewLine            if (inDict != null)Di2015NewLine                return dict[inDict];Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                int n = dict.Count;Di2015NewLine                dict[obj] = n;Di2015NewLine                return n;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }// classDi2015NewLine

4415542Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic DataTable RemoveDuplicateRows(DataTable dTable, string colName)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine   Hashtable hTable = new Hashtable();Di2015NewLine   ArrayList duplicateList = new ArrayList();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine   //Add list of all the unique item value to hashtable, which stores combination of key, value pair.Di2015NewLine   //And add duplicate item value in arraylist.Di2015NewLine   foreach (DataRow drow in dTable.Rows)Di2015NewLine   {Di2015NewLine      if (hTable.Contains(drow[colName]))Di2015NewLine         duplicateList.Add(drow);Di2015NewLine      elseDi2015NewLine         hTable.Add(drow[colName], string.Empty); Di2015NewLine   }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine   //Removing a list of duplicate items from datatable.Di2015NewLine   foreach (DataRow dRow in duplicateList)Di2015NewLine      dTable.Rows.Remove(dRow);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine   //Datatable which contains unique records will be return as output.Di2015NewLine      return dTable;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

null : "@using " + m.Groups["ns"].Value);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        //headersDi2015NewLine        string text3 = Regex.Replace(text2, @"<%@\\s(?<dir>.*?)%>", m =>  "@{ " + m.Groups["dir"].Value + "}"); // Preserves headersDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        //expressions Di2015NewLine        string text4 = Regex.Replace(text3, @"<%[=:](?<expr>.*?)%>", m =>Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            string expr = m.Groups["expr"].Value.Trim();Di2015NewLine            string cleanExpr = Regex.Replace(expr, @"(""(\\\\""|[^""])*"")|(@""([^""]|"""")*"")|(\\([^\\(\\)]*(((?'Open'\\()[^\\(\\)]*)+((?'Close-Open'\\))[^\\(\\)]*)+)*\\))", m2 => "");Di2015NewLine            return cleanExpr.Contains(' ') ? "@(" + expr + ")" : "@" + expr;Di2015NewLine        }, RegexOptions.Singleline);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        //code blocksDi2015NewLine        string text5 = Regex.Replace(text4, @"<%(?<code>.*?)%>", m =>Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            string code = m.Groups["code"].Value.Trim();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            Dictionary<string, string> stringLiterals = new Dictionary<string,string>();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            code = Regex.Replace(code, @"(""(\\\\""|[^""])*"")|(@""([^""]|"""")*"")", m2 =>Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                string key = "<$" + stringLiterals.Count + "$>";Di2015NewLine                stringLiterals.Add(key, m2.Value);Di2015NewLine                return key;Di2015NewLine            }); Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            string result = Regex.Replace(code, Di2015NewLine                @"((?<blockHeader>(else|(for|switch|foreach|using|while|if)\\s*\\([^\\(\\)]*(((?'Open'\\()[^\\(\\)]*)+((?'Close-Open'\\))[^\\(\\)]*)+)*\\))\\s*)" + Di2015NewLine                @"((?<fullBlock>{[^{}]*(((?'OpenCurly'{)[^{}]*)+((?'CloseCurly-OpenCurly'})[^{}]*)+)*})|(?<openblock>{.*))|" + Di2015NewLine                @"(?<text>((?!({|}|\\s)(for|switch|foreach|using|while|if|else)(\\s|{|\\()).)+))",Di2015NewLine                m2 =>Di2015NewLine                {Di2015NewLine                    if(m2.Value.Trim().Length == 0 || m2.Value.StartsWith("else")|| m2.Value.StartsWith("}"))Di2015NewLine                        return m2.Value;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine                    if(m2.Groups["text"].Success)Di2015NewLine                        return "@{ " + m2.Value.Trim() + "}\\r\\n"; Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine                    return "@" + m2.Value; Di2015NewLine                }, RegexOptions.ExplicitCapture | RegexOptions.Singleline);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            result = Regex.Replace(result, @"<\\$\\d+\\$>", Di2015NewLine                m2 => stringLiterals[m2.Value]);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine            return result;Di2015NewLine        }, RegexOptions.Singleline);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return text5; Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4425602Di2015UniqueSeparatorint[] orginalArray = { 10, 8, 6, 5, 3 };Di2015NewLineint[] copyArray = new int[orginalArray.Length];Di2015NewLineint[] resultArray = new int[orginalArray.Length];Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine// Make a copy of the orginal arrayDi2015NewLineArray.Copy(orginalArray,0, copyArray, 0,orginalArray.Length);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine// Sort the copied array in ascendng order (last 3 elements are the largest 3 elements)Di2015NewLineArray.Sort(copyArray);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine// Array to store the largest elementsDi2015NewLineint[] largest = new int[3];Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinefor (int i = copyArray.Length - 3, j = 0; i < copyArray.Length; i++, j++)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    largest[j] = copyArray[i];Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine// Sum of the largest elementsDi2015NewLineint largestSum = largest.Sum();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine// Copy the non largest elements to the result array (in the original order)Di2015NewLinefor (int i = 0, j=0; i < orginalArray.Length; i++)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    if (!largest.Contains(orginalArray[i]))Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        resultArray[j++] = orginalArray[i];Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine// Copy the largest elements to the last 3 positionsDi2015NewLinefor(int i=largest.Length - 1, j=0;i<resultArray.Length;i++, j++)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    resultArray[i] = largest[j];Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine// Result - resultArray[] : 5 3 6 8 10Di2015NewLine// Largest sum combination - largest[]: 6 8 10Di2015NewLine// Sum of largest combination - largestSum: 24Di2015NewLine

4430018Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static Expression<Func<T, bool>> OrTheseFiltersTogether<T>( Di2015NewLine  this IEnumerable<Expression<Func<T, bool>>> filters) Di2015NewLine{ Di2015NewLine    Expression<Func<T, bool>> firstFilter = filters.FirstOrDefault(); Di2015NewLine    if (firstFilter == null) Di2015NewLine    { Di2015NewLine        Expression<Func<T, bool>> alwaysTrue = x => true; Di2015NewLine        return alwaysTrue; Di2015NewLine    } Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    var body = firstFilter.Body; Di2015NewLine    var param = firstFilter.Parameters.ToArray(); Di2015NewLine    foreach (var nextFilter in filters.Skip(1)) Di2015NewLine    { Di2015NewLine        var nextBody = Expression.Invoke(nextFilter, param); Di2015NewLine        body = Expression.OrElse(body, nextBody); Di2015NewLine    } Di2015NewLine    Expression<Func<T, bool>> result = Expression.Lambda<Func<T, bool>>(body, param); Di2015NewLine    return result; Di2015NewLine} Di2015NewLine

4430760Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static void Swap<T>(ref T x, ref T y)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    T tmp = y;Di2015NewLine    y = x;Di2015NewLine    x = tmp;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineprivate void Draw3DLine(int x0, int y0, int z0, int x1, int y1, int z1)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    bool steepXY = Math.Abs(y1 - y0) > Math.Abs(x1 - x0);Di2015NewLine    if (steepXY) { Swap(ref x0, ref y0); Swap(ref x1, ref y1); }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    bool steepXZ = Math.Abs(z1 - z0) > Math.Abs(x1 - x0);Di2015NewLine    if (steepXZ) { Swap(ref x0, ref z0); Swap(ref x1, ref z1); }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    int deltaX = Math.Abs(x1 - x0);Di2015NewLine    int deltaY = Math.Abs(y1 - y0);Di2015NewLine    int deltaZ = Math.Abs(z1 - z0);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    int errorXY = deltaX / 2, errorXZ = deltaX / 2;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    int stepX = (x0 > x1) ? -1 : 1;  Di2015NewLine    int stepY = (y0 > y1) ? -1 : 1;Di2015NewLine    int stepZ = (z0 > z1) ? -1 : 1;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    int y=y0, z=z0;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Check if the end of the line hasn't been reached.Di2015NewLine    for(int x = x0; x!=x1; x+=stepX) Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int xCopy=x, yCopy=y, zCopy=z;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (steepXZ) Swap(ref xCopy, ref zCopy);Di2015NewLine        if (steepXY) Swap(ref xCopy, ref yCopy);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Replace the WriteLine with your call to DrawOneBlockDi2015NewLine        Console.WriteLine("[" + xCopy + ", " + yCopy + ", " + zCopy + "], ");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        errorXY -= deltaY;Di2015NewLine        errorXZ -= deltaZ;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (errorXY < 0) Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            y += stepY;Di2015NewLine            errorXY += deltaX;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (errorXZ < 0) Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            z += stepZ;Di2015NewLine            errorXZ += deltaX;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4432750Di2015UniqueSeparator// Make more general if you want, with parameters for the separator, length etcDi2015NewLinepublic static string PadCommaSeparated(string text)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    StringBuilder builder = new StringBuilder();Di2015NewLine    int start = 0;Di2015NewLine    int nextComma = text.IndexOf(',');Di2015NewLine    while (nextComma >= 0)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int itemLength = nextComma - start;Di2015NewLine        switch (itemLength)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            case 0:Di2015NewLine                builder.Append("00,");Di2015NewLine                break;Di2015NewLine            case 1:Di2015NewLine                builder.Append("0");Di2015NewLine                goto default;Di2015NewLine            default:Di2015NewLine                builder.Append(text, start, itemLength);Di2015NewLine                builder.Append(",");Di2015NewLine                break;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        start = nextComma + 1;Di2015NewLine        nextComma = text.IndexOf(',', start);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    // Now deal with the end...Di2015NewLine    int finalItemLength = text.Length - start;Di2015NewLine    switch (finalItemLength)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        case 0:Di2015NewLine            builder.Append("00");Di2015NewLine            break;Di2015NewLine        case 1:Di2015NewLine            builder.Append("0");Di2015NewLine            goto default;Di2015NewLine        default:Di2015NewLine            builder.Append(text, start, finalItemLength);Di2015NewLine            break;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    return builder.ToString();Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4434377Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static class MonadicArithmeticDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine   public static Monad Take(int input) { return new Monad(input); }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine   public class MonadDi2015NewLine   {Di2015NewLine      int theValue;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine      internal Monad(int input) { theValue = input; }   Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine      public Monad Add(int input){ return new Monad(theValue + input); }Di2015NewLine      public Monad Subtract(int input){ return new Monad(theValue - result); }Di2015NewLine      public int Value { get { return theValue; } }Di2015NewLine   }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine...Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine//usageDi2015NewLinevar result = MonadicArithmetic.Take(1).Add(2).Subtract(1).Value; //2Di2015NewLine
4434377Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static class MonadicArithmeticDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine   public static Monad Take(int input) { return new Monad(input); }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine   public class MonadDi2015NewLine   {Di2015NewLine      //Change the "value keeper" into a Func that will return the value;Di2015NewLine      Func<int> theValue;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine      //the constructor now turns the input value into a lambdaDi2015NewLine      internal Monad(int input) { theValue = ()=>input; }Di2015NewLine      //and another constructor is added for intra-class use that takes a lambda Di2015NewLine      private Monad(Func<int> input) { theValue = input; }   Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine      //And now the methods will create new lambdas that call the existing lambdasDi2015NewLine      public Monad Add(int input){ return new Monad(()=>theValue() + input); }Di2015NewLine      public Monad Subtract(int input){ return new Monad(()=>theValue() - input); }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine      //Finally, our Value getter at the end will evaluate the lambda, unwrapping all the nested callsDi2015NewLine      public int Value { get { return theValue(); } }Di2015NewLine   }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
4434377Di2015UniqueSeparator//Each call just adds a shell to the nested lambdasDi2015NewLinevar operation = MonadicArithmetic.Take(1).Add(2).Subtract(1);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine...Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine//HERE's the payoff; the result is not evaluated till the call to Value_get() behind the scenes of this assignment.Di2015NewLinevar result = operation.Value; Di2015NewLine
4434377Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static class MonadicArithmeticDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine   public static Monad Take(int input) { return new Monad(input); }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine   public class MonadDi2015NewLine   {Di2015NewLine      //Our value keeper is now a pure function that requires no external closuresDi2015NewLine      Func<Func<int>, int, int> operation;Di2015NewLine      //and we add two new private fields; Di2015NewLine      //a hook to a lambda that will give us the result of all previous operations,Di2015NewLine      Func<int> source;Di2015NewLine      //... and the value for the current operation.Di2015NewLine      private int addend;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine      //our constructor now takes the value, stores it, and creates a simple lambdaDi2015NewLine      internal Monad(int input) { addend = input; operation = ()=>addend; }Di2015NewLine      //and our private constructor now builds a new Monad from scratchDi2015NewLine      private Monad(Func<int> prevOp, Func<Func<int>, int, int> currOp, int input) Di2015NewLine      { Di2015NewLine          source = prevOp, Di2015NewLine          operation = currOp, Di2015NewLine          addend = input; Di2015NewLine      }  Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine      //The methods will create new Monads that take the current Monad's value getter,   Di2015NewLine      //keeping the current Monad in memory.Di2015NewLine      public Monad Add(int input)Di2015NewLine      { Di2015NewLine         return new Monad(this.Result, (f,i)=>f()+i, input); Di2015NewLine      }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine      public Monad Subtract(int input)Di2015NewLine      { Di2015NewLine         return new Monad(this.Result, (f,i)=>f()-i, input); Di2015NewLine      }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine      //And we change our property to a method, so it can also Di2015NewLine      //be used internally as a delegateDi2015NewLine      public int Result() { return operation(source, addend); }Di2015NewLine   }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine//usageDi2015NewLinevar operations = MonadicArithmetic.Take(1).Add(3).Subtract(2); Di2015NewLine//There are now 3 Monads in memory, each holding a hook to the previous Monad, Di2015NewLine//the current addend, and a function to produce the result...Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine...Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine//so that here, all the necessary pieces are still available.Di2015NewLinevar result = operations.Result();  Di2015NewLine

4463899Di2015UniqueSeparatorIf MyColor = 0xAABBCCDDDi2015NewLineAA = 170Di2015NewLineBB = 187Di2015NewLineCC = 204Di2015NewLineDD = 221Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineExpected values:Di2015NewLinebA = 170Di2015NewLinebR = 187 * (255 / 170) = 280.5Di2015NewLinebG = 204 * (255 / 170) = 306Di2015NewLinebB = 221 * (255 / 170) = 331.5 Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinewith integer division 255/170, 255/204, 255/221 will all evaluate to 1 and premultiplication becomes ineffective. Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineBy using this operation ai = ((255 << 8) / ai)   Di2015NewLinewith integer division: ai = (255*256)/170 = 384Di2015NewLineand subsequent multiplications and shifts gives you a more accurate result.Di2015NewLineE.g.Di2015NewLinebR = 187 * 384 / 256 =  280Di2015NewLinebG = 204 * 384 / 256 =  306Di2015NewLinebB = 221 * 384 / 256 =  331Di2015NewLine

4464962Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic class PriorityBlockingQueue<TKey, TValue>Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    private SortedDictionary<TKey, TValue> m_Dictionary = new SortedDictionary<TKey,TValue>();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public void Add(TKey key, TValue value)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        lock (m_Dictionary)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            m_Dictionary.Add(key, value);Di2015NewLine            Monitor.Pulse(m_Dictionary);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public TValue Take(TKey key)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        TValue value;Di2015NewLine        TryTake(key, TimeSpan.FromTicks(long.MaxValue), out value);Di2015NewLine        return value;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public bool TryTake(TKey key, TimeSpan timeout, out TValue value)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        value = default(TValue);Di2015NewLine        DateTime initial = DateTime.UtcNow;Di2015NewLine        lock (m_Dictionary)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            while (!m_Dictionary.TryGetValue(key, out value))Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                if (m_Dictionary.Count > 0) Monitor.Pulse(m_Dictionary); // Important!Di2015NewLine                TimeSpan span = timeout - (DateTime.UtcNow - initial);Di2015NewLine                if (!Monitor.Wait(m_Dictionary, span))Di2015NewLine                {Di2015NewLine                    return false;Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            m_Dictionary.Remove(key);Di2015NewLine            return true;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4490464Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic long Prod2(long u, long v)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    int n = Math.Max((int)Math.Floor(Math.Log10(u) + 1), (int)Math.Floor(Math.Log10(v) + 1));Di2015NewLine    int threshold = 3;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if(u == 0 || v == 0)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return 0;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    else if(n <= threshold)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return u * v;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    elseDi2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int m = (int)Math.Ceiling(n / 2.0);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        int x = (int)(u / Math.Pow(10, m));Di2015NewLine        int y = (int)(u % Math.Pow(10, m));Di2015NewLine        int w = (int)(u / Math.Pow(10, m));Di2015NewLine        int z = (int)(v % Math.Pow(10, m));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        long r = Prod2(x + y, w + z);Di2015NewLine        long p = Prod2(x, w);Di2015NewLine        long q = Prod2(y, z);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return p * (long)Math.Pow(10, 2 * m) + (r - p - q) * (long)Math.Pow(10, m) + q;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4492527Di2015UniqueSeparatorusing namespace System;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine#include "myAlgorithmClass"Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinepublic ref class MyCLIWrapperClass //the 'ref' keyword specifies that this is a managed classDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLinepublic:Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    MyCLIWrapperClass(); //ConstructorDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    //function definitions are the same, though some types,Di2015NewLine    //like string, change a little. Here's an example:Di2015NewLine    String ^ GetAString(); //the "String" is the .NET "System.String" and the ^ is sort of a pointer for managed classesDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    //int, double, long, char, etc do not need to be specified as managed.Di2015NewLine    //.NET code will know how to handle these types.Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    //Here you want to define some functions in the wrapper that will callDi2015NewLine    //the functions from your un-managed class. Here are some examples:Di2015NewLine    //Say that your functions in the Algorithm class are int Func1, double Func2, and std::string Func3:Di2015NewLine    int Func1();Di2015NewLine    double Func2();Di2015NewLine    String ^ Func3();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineprivate:Di2015NewLine    //All private functions and members hereDi2015NewLine    myAlgorithmClass algor;Di2015NewLine};Di2015NewLine
4492527Di2015UniqueSeparatorusing namespace System;Di2015NewLine#include <string> //For the string function ex. belowDi2015NewLine#include "myAlgorithmClass"Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineMyCLIWrapperClass::MyCLIWrapperClass()Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    algor = myAlgorithmClass(); //create instance of your un-managed classDi2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineint MyCLIWrapperClass::Func1()Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    return algor.Func1(); //Call the un-managed class function.Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinedouble MyCLIWrapperClass::Func2()Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    return algor.Func2(); //Call the un-managed class function.Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineString ^ MyCLIWrapperClass::Func3()Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    //Converting a std::string to a System.String requires some conversionDi2015NewLine    //but I'm sure you can find that somewhere on Google or here on SODi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    String ^ myString = "";Di2015NewLine    std::string myUnmanagedString = algor.Func3(); //Call the un-managed class function.Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    //Convert myUnmanagedString from std::string to System.String hereDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return myString;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

First emumerate the windows and running Di2015NewLine// programs and then see which events should be run.Di2015NewLine// this function must not run if blocked, 'once' countdownDi2015NewLine// has run out, or stopscript=1, or entry = 1Di2015NewLinevoid RunEvents(void)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine// Please keep in mind this program's error philosphoy whenDi2015NewLine// extending it, namely, catch all possible script errorsDi2015NewLine// when loading script, but do not display messageboxes forDi2015NewLine// even the most serious errors when doing events, because Di2015NewLine// the idea is to catch errors during development and avoidDi2015NewLine// errors at run time or in production!!Di2015NewLine static bEventEntry=0;Di2015NewLine WindowList_t *wl;Di2015NewLine EventList_t *el;Di2015NewLine ParmList_t *pl;Di2015NewLine char *st;Di2015NewLine int i;Di2015NewLine long lExitCode;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine // exit this routine if we shouldn't be hereDi2015NewLine    if (g_iStopScript || bEventEntry)Di2015NewLine  return;Di2015NewLine bEventEntry=1;Di2015NewLine // clear all of the window handles in windowobject listDi2015NewLine for (wl=g_windowlist;wl;wl=wl->next)Di2015NewLine {Di2015NewLine  wl->hwnd=NULL;Di2015NewLine  wl->bWarned = 0;Di2015NewLine }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine // enumerate all windows in the system; repopulate all ofDi2015NewLine // the window handles in the windowobject listDi2015NewLine EnumWindows(EnumWindowProc4Search,0);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine // go thru event list, calling any events that must Di2015NewLine // be called; windows handles for any subsequent actionsDi2015NewLine // will have been set by above code. Check for runs endingDi2015NewLine // to process runend events and search the windowobject listDi2015NewLine // to process windowopen events. Di2015NewLine for (el=g_eventlist;g_eventlist && el;el=el->next)Di2015NewLine {Di2015NewLine  pl=MakeParms(el->stEventTypeSourceLine);Di2015NewLine  st=ParmValue(pl,2); // event nameDi2015NewLine  // check for windowopen eventsDi2015NewLine  if (el->iEventType==ET_WINDOWOPEN)Di2015NewLine  { // search for their open windows!!Di2015NewLine   for (wl=g_windowlist;wl;wl=wl->next)Di2015NewLine   {Di2015NewLine    if (0==_stricmp(wl->stName,st) && wl->hwnd)Di2015NewLine     RunActions(el);Di2015NewLine    if (g_iStopScript)Di2015NewLine     return; // quit doing actions/events ASAP.  }Di2015NewLine   }Di2015NewLine  }Di2015NewLine  if (el->iEventType==ET_RUNEND)Di2015NewLine  {Di2015NewLine   sscanf(st,"%ld",&i);Di2015NewLine   if (g_runids[i]!=-1 && g_runids[i]!=0)Di2015NewLine   {Di2015NewLine    GetExitCodeProcess((HANDLE)g_runids[i],&lExitCode);Di2015NewLine    if (lExitCode != STILL_ACTIVE) Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine     RunActions(el);Di2015NewLine     g_runids[i]=0;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine   }Di2015NewLine  }Di2015NewLine  KillParms(pl);Di2015NewLine }Di2015NewLine bEventEntry=0;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinevoid RunStartup(void)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine EventList_t *el;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (bEventEntry)Di2015NewLine  return;Di2015NewLine bEventEntry=1;Di2015NewLine // check stopscript in case of endscript in startup event!Di2015NewLine for (el=g_eventlist;g_eventlist && el && !g_iStopScript;el=el->next)Di2015NewLine {Di2015NewLine  if (el->iEventType==ET_STARTUP)Di2015NewLine   RunActions(el);Di2015NewLine }Di2015NewLine bEventEntry=0;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4519887Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate class NodeDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    public string Value { get; private set; }Di2015NewLine    public Node Parent { get; private set; }Di2015NewLine    public List<Node> Children { get; private set; }Di2015NewLine    public Node(string c, Node parent)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        this.Value = c;Di2015NewLine        this.Parent = parent;Di2015NewLine        this.Children = new List<Node>();Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    public override string ToString()Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return "Value: " + this.Value;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineprivate static Node BuildTree(IEnumerable<string> tokens, char[] sep)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    var root = new Node(null, null);Di2015NewLine    foreach (var token in tokens)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine#if OLDVERSIONDi2015NewLine        var current = root;Di2015NewLine        var splits = token.Split(sep);Di2015NewLine#elseDi2015NewLine        var splits = token.Split(sep);Di2015NewLine        var current = FindFirstNodeWithValue(root, splits.First());Di2015NewLine        if (current == null)Di2015NewLine            current = root;Di2015NewLine        elseDi2015NewLine            current = current.Parent;Di2015NewLine#endifDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; 4526075Di2015UniqueSeparator    private static int CompareTabIndex(TextBox c1, TextBox c2)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return c1.TabIndex.CompareTo(c2.TabIndex);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public static bool IsValid(Form form)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        List<TextBox> textBoxes = new List<TextBox>();Di2015NewLine        foreach(Control ctl in form.Controls)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            TextBox textBox = ctl as TextBox;Di2015NewLine            if(textBox != null) textBoxes.Add(textBox);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        textBoxes.Sort(new Comparison<TextBox>(CompareTabIndex));Di2015NewLine        foreach(TextBox textBox in textBoxes)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if(textBox.AccessibleDescription == "Valid" && textBox.Text.Trim() == "")Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                MessageBox.Show(textBox.AccessibleName + " Can't be Blank",Di2015NewLine                    Program.companyName, MessageBoxButtons.OK, MessageBoxIcon.Stop);Di2015NewLine                textBox.Focus();Di2015NewLine                return false;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return true;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine
4526387Di2015UniqueSeparatorString
4526387Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static IEnumerable<string> GetPages(this string text, Di2015NewLine    int charsPerPage, string breakChar)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    int count = 0;Di2015NewLine    int start = 0;Di2015NewLine    while (count < text.Length)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        count = Math.Min(text.Length, count + charsPerPage);Di2015NewLine        if (count == text.Length)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            yield return text.Substring(start, count - start);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        elseDi2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            var nextBreak = text.IndexOf(breakChar, count);Di2015NewLine            if (nextBreak == -1)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                yield return text.Substring(start, count - start);Di2015NewLine                start = count + breakChar.Length;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                yield return text.Substring(start, nextBreak - start);Di2015NewLine                start = nextBreak + breakChar.Length;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4529688Di2015UniqueSeparatorSystem.Collections.Generic.Dictionary<string, string> hashTable = new System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary<string, string>();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLinestring myString = "Type=\\"Category\\" Position=\\"Top\\" Child=\\"3\\"";Di2015NewLinestring pattern = @"([A-Za-z0-9]+)(\\s*)(=)(\\s*)("")([^""]*)("")";Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineSystem.Text.RegularExpressions.MatchCollection matches = System.Text.RegularExpressions.Regex.Matches(myString, pattern);Di2015NewLineforeach (System.Text.RegularExpressions.Match m in matches)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    string key = m.Groups[1].Value;    // ([A-Za-z0-9]+)Di2015NewLine    string value = m.Groups[6].Value;    // ([^""]*)Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    hashTable[key] = value;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
4529724Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate static int CalcLevensteinDistance(string left, string right)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    if (left == right)Di2015NewLine        return 0;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    int[,] matrix = new int[left.Length + 1, right.Length + 1];Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    for (int i = 0; i <= left.Length; i++)Di2015NewLine        // deleteDi2015NewLine        matrix[i, 0] = i;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    for (int j = 0; j <= right.Length; j++)Di2015NewLine        // insertDi2015NewLine        matrix[0, j] = j;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    for (int i = 0; i < left.Length; i++)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        for (int j = 0; j < right.Length; j++)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            if (left[i] == right[j])Di2015NewLine                matrix[i + 1, j + 1] = matrix[i, j];Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                // deletion or insertionDi2015NewLine                matrix[i + 1, j + 1] = System.Math.Min(matrix[i, j + 1] + 1, matrix[i + 1, j] + 1);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine                // substitutionDi2015NewLine                matrix[i + 1, j + 1] = System.Math.Min(matrix[i + 1, j + 1], matrix[i, j] + 1);Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return matrix[left.Length, right.Length];Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
4529724Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static double CalcSimilarity(string left, string right, bool ignoreCase)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    if (ignoreCase)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        left = left.ToLower();Di2015NewLine        right = right.ToLower();Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    double distance = CalcLevensteinDistance(left, right);Di2015NewLine    if (distance == 0.0f)Di2015NewLine        return 1.0f;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    double longestStringSize = System.Math.Max(left.Length, right.Length);Di2015NewLine    double percent = distance / longestStringSize;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return 1.0f - percent;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4531131Di2015UniqueSeparator public int binarysearch(int searchnum)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        string[] source = textBox1.Text.Split(',');Di2015NewLine        int[] nums = new int[source.Length];Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i < source.Length; i++)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            nums[i] = Convert.ToInt32(source[i]);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        int first = 0;Di2015NewLine        int last = nums.Length - 1;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        while (1 <= nums.Length)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            int mid = (int)Math.Floor((first + last) / 2.0);Di2015NewLine            if (first > last)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                break;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            if (searchnum < nums[mid])Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                last = mid - 1;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            if (searchnum > nums[mid])Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                first = mid + 1;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            if (searchnum == nums[mid])Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                return nums[mid];Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return -1;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine

4541907Di2015UniqueSeparator        /// <summary>Di2015NewLine    /// Based on the 2d line intersection method from "comp.graphics.algorithms Frequently Asked Questions"Di2015NewLine    /// </summary>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="currentLocation">The current location.</param>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="requestedLocation">The requested location.</param>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="boundary">The boundary.</param>Di2015NewLine    /// <param name="collisionVector">The collision vector.</param>Di2015NewLine    /// <returns></returns>Di2015NewLine    public static bool Intersects(Vector2 currentLocation, Vector2 requestedLocation, Boundary boundary, ref Vector2 collisionVector)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        float q = (currentLocation.Y - boundary.Start.Y) * (boundary.End.X - boundary.Start.X) - (currentLocation.X - boundary.Start.X) * (boundary.End.Y - boundary.Start.Y);Di2015NewLine        float d = (requestedLocation.X - currentLocation.X) * (boundary.End.Y - boundary.Start.Y) - (requestedLocation.Y - currentLocation.Y) * (boundary.End.X - boundary.Start.X);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (d == 0) Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            return false;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        float r = q / d;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        q = (currentLocation.Y - boundary.Start.Y) * (requestedLocation.X - currentLocation.X) - (currentLocation.X - boundary.Start.X) * (requestedLocation.Y - currentLocation.Y);Di2015NewLine        float s = q / d;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (r < 0 || r > 1 || s < 0 || s > 1)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            return false;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        collisionVector.X = currentLocation.X + (int)(0.5f + r * (requestedLocation.X - currentLocation.X));Di2015NewLine        collisionVector.Y = currentLocation.Y + (int)(0.5f + r * (requestedLocation.Y - currentLocation.Y));Di2015NewLine        return true;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine

4547030Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static void WriteElementContent(this XmlWriter writer, string content)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    if (String.IsNullOrEmpty(content))Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // WriteString will happily escape any XML markup characters. 4549500Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic int GetFactorCount(int numberToCheck)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    int factorCount = 0;Di2015NewLine    int sqrt = (int)Math.Ceiling(Math.Sqrt(numberToCheck));Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Start from 1 as we want our method to also work when numberToCheck is 0 or 1.Di2015NewLine    for (int i = 1; i < sqrt; i++)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        if (numberToCheck % i == 0)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            factorCount += 2; //  We found a pair of factors.Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Check if our number is an exact square.Di2015NewLine    if (sqrt * sqrt == numberToCheck)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        factorCount++;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    return factorCount;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4554954Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate void drawCurvedLine()Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    //initialise the plot area:Di2015NewLine    Bitmap image = new Bitmap(pictureBox1.Width, pictureBox1.Height);Di2015NewLine    pictureBox1.BackgroundImage = image;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    using(Graphics g = Graphics.FromImage(image))Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        PointF[] points = new PointF[4];Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        //first straight:Di2015NewLine        points[0] = new PointF(287.284149F, 21.236269F);Di2015NewLine        points[1] = new PointF(183.638443F, 406.936249F);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        //second straight:Di2015NewLine        points[2] = new PointF(130.842773F, 515.574036F);Di2015NewLine        points[3] = new PointF(-1950.91321F, 3491.868F);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        //graphics path for the line:Di2015NewLine        using(GraphicsPath gPath = new GraphicsPath())Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            gPath.AddLine(points[0], points[1]);Di2015NewLine            gPath.AddArc(new RectangleF(-445.464447F, 3.84924316F, 640.067444F, 640.067444F), -(90 - 4564045Di2015UniqueSeparatorstatic Int32 GetYearFromBCD(Int32 time)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    List<Int32> YearList = new List<Int32>();Di2015NewLine    for (Int32 i = 3; i >= 0; i --)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        Int32 place = i * 4;Di2015NewLine        Int32 val = 0x01 << place;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        Int32 curVal = (Int32)(time / val);Di2015NewLine        if (curVal > 9 && YearList.Count > 0)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            Int32 delta = (Int32)(curVal / 10);Di2015NewLine            YearList[YearList.Count - 1] += delta;Di2015NewLine            curVal -= delta * 10;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        YearList.Add(curVal);Di2015NewLine        time -= curVal << place;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    Int32 Year = 0;Di2015NewLine    for (Int32 y = 0; y < 4; y++)Di2015NewLine        Year += YearList[y] * (Int32)Math.Pow(10,(4 - y)-1);Di2015NewLine    return Year;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4571792Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static bool CompareArraysExhaustively(byte[] first, byte[] second)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    if (first.Length != second.Length)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return false;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    bool ret = true;Di2015NewLine    for (int i = 0; i < first.Length; i++)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        ret = ret & (first[i] == second[i]);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    return ret;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4571792Di2015UniqueSeparatorstatic bool VerifyIntegrity(string secret, string checksum, string data)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    // Verify HMAC-SHA256 ChecksumDi2015NewLine    byte[] key = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(secret);Di2015NewLine    byte[] value = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(data);Di2015NewLine    byte[] checksumBytes = Convert.FromBase64String(checksum);Di2015NewLine    using (var hmac = new HMACSHA256(key))Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        byte[] expectedBytes = hmac.ComputeHash(value);Di2015NewLine        return checksumBytes.SequenceEqual(expectedBytes);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
4571792Di2015UniqueSeparatorstatic bool VerifyIntegrity(string secret, string checksum, string data)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    // Verify HMAC-SHA256 ChecksumDi2015NewLine    byte[] key = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(secret);Di2015NewLine    byte[] value = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(data);Di2015NewLine    using (var hmac = new HMACSHA256(key))Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return checksum == Convert.ToBase64String(hmac.ComputeHash(value));Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4577922Di2015UniqueSeparatorstatic IEnumerable<T> MergeShuffle<T>(IEnumerable<T> lista, IEnumerable<T> listb)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    var first = lista.GetEnumerator();Di2015NewLine    var second = listb.GetEnumerator();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    var rand = new Random();Di2015NewLine    bool exhaustedA = false;Di2015NewLine    bool exhaustedB = false;Di2015NewLine    while (!(exhaustedA && exhaustedB))Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        bool found = false;Di2015NewLine        if (!exhaustedB && (exhaustedA || rand.Next(0, 2) == 0))Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine             exhaustedB = !(found = second.MoveNext());Di2015NewLine            if (found)Di2015NewLine                yield return second.Current;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        if (!found && !exhaustedA)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            exhaustedA = !(found = first.MoveNext());Di2015NewLine            if (found)Di2015NewLine                yield return first.Current;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }                Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
4577922Di2015UniqueSeparator    static IEnumerable<T> MergeShuffle<T>(IEnumerable<T> lista, IEnumerable<T> listb)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        int total = lista.Count() + listb.Count();Di2015NewLine        var random = new Random();Di2015NewLine        var indexes = Enumerable.Range(0, total-1)Di2015NewLine                                .OrderBy(_=>random.NextDouble())Di2015NewLine                                .Take(lista.Count())Di2015NewLine                                .OrderBy(x=>x)Di2015NewLine                                .ToList();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        var first = lista.GetEnumerator();Di2015NewLine        var second = listb.GetEnumerator();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i < total; i++)Di2015NewLine            if (indexes.Contains(i))Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                first.MoveNext();Di2015NewLine                yield return first.Current;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            elseDi2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                second.MoveNext();Di2015NewLine                yield return second.Current;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine

4591150Di2015UniqueSeparatorstatic class MapCopierDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    public static void Copy(IEnumerable<IUntypedField> fields, IFieldMap from, IFieldMap to)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        foreach (var field in fields)Di2015NewLine            Copy(field, from, to);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // cache generated Copy lambdasDi2015NewLine    static Dictionary<Type, Action<IUntypedField, IFieldMap, IFieldMap>> copiers =Di2015NewLine        new Dictionary<Type, Action<IUntypedField, IFieldMap, IFieldMap>>();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // generate Copy lambda based on passed-in typeDi2015NewLine    static void Copy(IUntypedField field, IFieldMap from, IFieldMap to)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        // figure out what type we need to look up;Di2015NewLine        // we know we have a Field<TValue>, so find TValueDi2015NewLine        Type type = field.GetType().GetGenericArguments()[0];Di2015NewLine        Action<IUntypedField, IFieldMap, IFieldMap> copier;Di2015NewLine        if (!copiers.TryGetValue(type, out copier))Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            // copier not found; create a lambda and compile itDi2015NewLine            Type tFieldMap = typeof(IFieldMap);Di2015NewLine            // create parameters to lambdaDi2015NewLine            ParameterExpressionDi2015NewLine                fieldParam = Expression.Parameter(typeof(IUntypedField)),Di2015NewLine                fromParam = Expression.Parameter(tFieldMap),Di2015NewLine                toParam = Expression.Parameter(tFieldMap);Di2015NewLine            // create expression for "(Field<TValue>)field"Di2015NewLine            var converter = Expression.Convert(fieldParam, field.GetType());Di2015NewLine            // create expression for "to.Put(field, from.Get(field))"Di2015NewLine            var copierExp =Di2015NewLine                Expression.Call(Di2015NewLine                    toParam,Di2015NewLine                    tFieldMap.GetMethod("Put").MakeGenericMethod(type),Di2015NewLine                    converter,Di2015NewLine                    Expression.Call(Di2015NewLine                        fromParam,Di2015NewLine                        tFieldMap.GetMethod("Get").MakeGenericMethod(type),Di2015NewLine                        converter));Di2015NewLine            // create our lambda and compile itDi2015NewLine            copier =Di2015NewLine                Expression.Lambda<Action<IUntypedField, IFieldMap, IFieldMap>>(Di2015NewLine                    copierExp,Di2015NewLine                    fieldParam,Di2015NewLine                    fromParam,Di2015NewLine                    toParam)Di2015NewLine                    .Compile();Di2015NewLine            // add the compiled lambda to the cacheDi2015NewLine            copiers[type] = copier;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        // invoke the actual copy lambdaDi2015NewLine        copier(field, from, to);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public static void Copy<TValue>(Field<TValue> field, IFieldMap from, IFieldMap to)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        to.Put(field, from.Get(field));Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

       Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public bool Equals(T[] x, T[] y)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        if (x == y)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            return true;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        if (x == null || y == null)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            return false;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        if (x.Length != y.Length)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            return false;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; 4601420Di2015UniqueSeparator        Random randF = new Random();Di2015NewLine        List<double> nums = new List<double>();Di2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i < 100000; i++)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            nums.Add(randF.NextDouble()*100);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        double fromXF = 30;Di2015NewLine        double toXF = 80;Di2015NewLine        int groupCount = 10; // number of groups between valuesDi2015NewLine        var histF = from i in numsDi2015NewLine                    let groupKeyF = ((i-fromXF)/(toXF-fromXF)*groupCount) // even distribution of "groupCount" groups between fromXF and toXF, simple math, reallyDi2015NewLine                    where groupKeyF >= 0 && groupKeyF < groupCount // only groups we wantDi2015NewLine                    let groupKey = (int)groupKeyF // clamp it to only group numberDi2015NewLine                    group i by groupKey into gr  // group it according to group numberDi2015NewLine                    orderby gr.KeyDi2015NewLine                    select new { Value = gr.Key, Count = gr.Count() };Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        foreach (var item in histF)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            Console.WriteLine("Group number: " + item.Value + ", Count: " + item.Count);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine

4601910Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate void CompareXml(string file1, string file2)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    // Load the documentsDi2015NewLine    XmlDocument docXml1 = new XmlDocument();Di2015NewLine    docXml1.Load(file1);Di2015NewLine    XmlDocument docXml2 = new XmlDocument();Di2015NewLine    docXml2.Load(file2);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Get a list of all player nodesDi2015NewLine    XmlNodeList nodes1 = docXml1.SelectNodes("/Stats/Player");Di2015NewLine    XmlNodeList nodes2 = docXml2.SelectNodes("/Stats/Player");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Define a single nodeDi2015NewLine    XmlNode node1;Di2015NewLine    XmlNode node2;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Get the root Xml elementDi2015NewLine    XmlElement root1 = docXml1.DocumentElement;Di2015NewLine    XmlElement root2 = docXml2.DocumentElement;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Get a list of all player namesDi2015NewLine    XmlNodeList nameList1 = root1.GetElementsByTagName("Name");Di2015NewLine    XmlNodeList nameList2 = root2.GetElementsByTagName("Name");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Get a list of all teamsDi2015NewLine    XmlNodeList teamList1 = root1.GetElementsByTagName("Team");Di2015NewLine    XmlNodeList teamList2 = root2.GetElementsByTagName("Team");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Create an XmlWriterSettings object with the correct options. Di2015NewLine    XmlWriter writer = null;Di2015NewLine    XmlWriterSettings settings = new XmlWriterSettings();Di2015NewLine    settings.Indent = true;Di2015NewLine    settings.IndentChars = ("  ");Di2015NewLine    settings.OmitXmlDeclaration = false;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Create the XmlWriter object and write some content.Di2015NewLine    writer = XmlWriter.Create(StatsFile.XmlDiffFilename, settings);Di2015NewLine    writer.WriteStartElement("StatsDiff");Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // The compare algorithmDi2015NewLine    bool match = false;Di2015NewLine    int j = 0;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    try Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        // the list has 500 playersDi2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i < 500; i++)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            while (j < 500 && match == false)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                // There is a match if the player name and team are the same in both listsDi2015NewLine                if (nameList1.Item(i).InnerText == nameList2.Item(j).InnerText)Di2015NewLine                {Di2015NewLine                    if (teamList1.Item(i).InnerText == teamList2.Item(j).InnerText)Di2015NewLine                    {Di2015NewLine                        match = true;Di2015NewLine                        node1 = nodes1.Item(i);Di2015NewLine                        node2 = nodes2.Item(j);Di2015NewLine                        // Call to the calculator and Xml writerDi2015NewLine                        this.CalculateDifferential(node1, node2, writer);Di2015NewLine                        j = 0;Di2015NewLine                    }Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLine                elseDi2015NewLine                {Di2015NewLine                    j++;Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            match = false;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        // end Xml documentDi2015NewLine        writer.WriteEndElement();Di2015NewLine        writer.Flush();Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    finallyDi2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        if (writer != null)Di2015NewLine            writer.Close();Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4602535Di2015UniqueSeparatorclass Converter<TTo>Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    class ConversionVisitor : ExpressionVisitorDi2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        private readonly ParameterExpression newParameter;Di2015NewLine        private readonly ParameterExpression oldParameter;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        public ConversionVisitor(ParameterExpression newParameter, ParameterExpression oldParameter)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            this.newParameter = newParameter;Di2015NewLine            this.oldParameter = oldParameter;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        protected override Expression VisitParameter(ParameterExpression node)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            return newParameter;                             });Di2015NewLine                                        //If context null raise Tick event from current threadDi2015NewLine                                        if (context == null)Di2015NewLine                                            callback(null);Di2015NewLine                                        elseDi2015NewLine 4610990Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic static class XmlWriterExtensionsDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    private static readonly Func<XmlWriter, object> get_writer;Di2015NewLine    private static readonly Func<object, char[]> get_bufChars;Di2015NewLine    private static readonly Func<object, int> get_bufPos;Di2015NewLine    private static readonly Action<object, int> set_bufPos;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    static XmlWriterExtensions()Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var asm = Assembly.GetAssembly(typeof(XmlWriter));Di2015NewLine        var xmlWellFormedWriterType = asm.GetType("System.Xml.XmlWellFormedWriter");Di2015NewLine        var flags = BindingFlags.NonPublic | BindingFlags.Instance;Di2015NewLine        var writerField = xmlWellFormedWriterType.GetField("writer", flags);Di2015NewLine        get_writer = w => writerField.GetValue(w);Di2015NewLine        var xmlEncodedRawTextWriterType = asm.GetType("System.Xml.XmlEncodedRawTextWriter");Di2015NewLine        var bufCharsField = xmlEncodedRawTextWriterType.GetField("bufChars", flags);Di2015NewLine        var bufPosField = xmlEncodedRawTextWriterType.GetField("bufPos", flags);Di2015NewLine        get_bufChars = w => (char[])bufCharsField.GetValue(w);Di2015NewLine        get_bufPos = w => (int)bufPosField.GetValue(w);Di2015NewLine        set_bufPos = (w, i) => bufPosField.SetValue(w, i);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public static void TrimElementEnd(this XmlWriter writer)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var internalWriter = get_writer(writer);Di2015NewLine        char[] bufChars = get_bufChars(internalWriter);Di2015NewLine        int bufPos = get_bufPos(internalWriter);Di2015NewLine        if (bufPos > 3 && bufChars[bufPos - 3] == ' ' && bufChars[bufPos - 2] == '/' && bufChars[bufPos - 1] == '>')Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            bufChars[bufPos - 3] = '/';Di2015NewLine            bufChars[bufPos - 2] = '>';Di2015NewLine            bufPos--;Di2015NewLine            set_bufPos(internalWriter, bufPos);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine// usage:Di2015NewLineConsole.OutputEncoding = Encoding.UTF8;Di2015NewLineusing (var writer = XmlWriter.Create(Console.Out))Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    writer.WriteStartElement("Foo");Di2015NewLine    writer.WriteElementString("Bar", null);Di2015NewLine    writer.TrimElementEnd();Di2015NewLine    writer.WriteElementString("Baz", null);Di2015NewLine    writer.WriteEndElement();Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4618750Di2015UniqueSeparator   function convertString(phrase)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    var maxLength = 100;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    var returnString = phrase.toLowerCase();Di2015NewLine    //Convert CharactersDi2015NewLine    returnString = returnString.replace(//g, 'o');Di2015NewLine    returnString = returnString.replace(//g, 'c');Di2015NewLine    returnString = returnString.replace(//g, 's');Di2015NewLine    returnString = returnString.replace(//g, 'i');Di2015NewLine    returnString = returnString.replace(//g, 'g');Di2015NewLine    returnString = returnString.replace(//g, 'u');  Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // if there are other invalid chars, convert them into blank spacesDi2015NewLine    returnString = returnString.replace(/[^a-z0-9\\s-]/g, "");Di2015NewLine    // convert multiple spaces and hyphens into one space       Di2015NewLine    returnString = returnString.replace(/[\\s-]+/g, " ");Di2015NewLine    // trims current stringDi2015NewLine    returnString = returnString.replace(/^\\s+|\\s+$/g,"");Di2015NewLine    // cuts string (if too long)Di2015NewLine    if(returnString.length > maxLength)Di2015NewLine    returnString = returnString.substring(0,maxLength);Di2015NewLine    // add hyphensDi2015NewLine    returnString = returnString.replace(/\\s/g, "-");  Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    alert(returnString);Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4619770Di2015UniqueSeparator///<summary>Returns the end of a text reader.</summary>Di2015NewLine///<param name="reader">The reader to read from.</param>Di2015NewLine///<param name="lineCount">The number of lines to return.</param>Di2015NewLine///<returns>The last lneCount lines from the reader.</returns>Di2015NewLinepublic static string[] Tail(this TextReader reader, int lineCount) {Di2015NewLine    var buffer = new List<string>(lineCount);Di2015NewLine    string line;Di2015NewLine    for (int i = 0; i < lineCount; i++) {Di2015NewLine        line = reader.ReadLine();Di2015NewLine        if (line == null) return buffer.ToArray();Di2015NewLine        buffer.Add(line);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    int lastLine = lineCount - 1;           //The index of the last line read from the buffer.  Everything > this index was read earlier than everything <= this indesDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    while (null != (line = reader.ReadLine())) {Di2015NewLine        lastLine++;Di2015NewLine        if (lastLine == lineCount) lastLine = 0;Di2015NewLine        buffer[lastLine] = line;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    if (lastLine == lineCount - 1) return buffer.ToArray();Di2015NewLine    var retVal = new string[lineCount];Di2015NewLine    buffer.CopyTo(lastLine + 1, retVal, 0, lineCount - lastLine - 1);Di2015NewLine    buffer.CopyTo(0, retVal, lineCount - lastLine - 1, lastLine + 1);Di2015NewLine    return retVal;Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4620495Di2015UniqueSeparator    public bool ConnectToAPNS()Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        X509Certificate2Collection certs = new X509Certificate2Collection();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine      apsHost = "gateway.sandbox.push.apple.com";Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Create a TCP socket connection to the Apple server on port 2195Di2015NewLine        TcpClient tcpClient = new false);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        //PushMessage();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return true;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private X509Certificate             {Di2015NewLine                        //Cert found, so return it.Di2015NewLine                        return certs[i];Di2015NewLine                    }Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            return test;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine        return test;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    private static byte[] HexToData(string hexString)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        if (hexString == null)Di2015NewLine            return null;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        if (hexString.Length % 2 == 1)Di2015NewLine            hexString = '0' + hexString; // Up to you whether to pad the first or last byteDi2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        byte[] data = new byte[hexString.Length / 2];Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        for (int i = 0; i < data.Length; i++)Di2015NewLine            data[i] = Convert.ToByte(hexString.Substring(i * 2, 2), 16);Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return data;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public bool PushMessage(string token, string message)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        String cToken = token;Di2015NewLine        String cAlert = message;Di2015NewLine        int iBadge = 1;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Ready to create the push notificationDi2015NewLine        byte[] buf = new byte[256];Di2015NewLine an audio file saved in the application bundle on the deviceDi2015NewLine        string msg = "{\\"aps\\":{\\"alert\\":\\"" + cAlert + "\\",\\"badge\\":" + iBadge.ToString() + ",\\"sound\\":\\"new.caf\\"}}";Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        // Write the data out to the streamDi2015NewLine        bw.Write((byte)msg.Length);Di2015NewLine sslStream.Write(ms.ToArray());Di2015NewLine            return true;Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine        return false;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine

4620799Di2015UniqueSeparatorEqualsHelper
4620799Di2015UniqueSeparatorprivate static unsafe bool EqualsHelper(string strA, string strB)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    int length = strA.Length;Di2015NewLine    if (length != strB.Length)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        return false;Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    fixed (char* chRef = &strA.m_firstChar)Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        fixed (char* chRef2 = &strB.m_firstChar)Di2015NewLine        {Di2015NewLine            char* chPtr = chRef;Di2015NewLine            char* chPtr2 = chRef2;Di2015NewLine            while (length >= 10)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                if ((((*(((int*) chPtr)) != *(((int*) chPtr2))) || (*(((int*) (chPtr + 2))) != *(((int*) (chPtr2 + 2))))) || ((*(((int*) (chPtr + 4))) != *(((int*) (chPtr2 + 4)))) || (*(((int*) (chPtr + 6))) != *(((int*) (chPtr2 + 6)))))) || (*(((int*) (chPtr + 8))) != *(((int*) (chPtr2 + 8)))))Di2015NewLine                {Di2015NewLine                    break;Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLine                chPtr += 10;Di2015NewLine                chPtr2 += 10;Di2015NewLine                length -= 10;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            while (length > 0)Di2015NewLine            {Di2015NewLine                if (*(((int*) chPtr)) != *(((int*) chPtr2)))Di2015NewLine                {Di2015NewLine                    break;Di2015NewLine                }Di2015NewLine                chPtr += 2;Di2015NewLine                chPtr2 += 2;Di2015NewLine                length -= 2;Di2015NewLine            }Di2015NewLine            return (length <= 0);Di2015NewLine        }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4621212Di2015UniqueSeparatorstatic void Main(string[] args)Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    string imageUrl = "http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/47/PNG_transparency_demonstration_1.png";Di2015NewLine    byte[] pngSignature = new byte[] { 137, 80, 78, 71, 13, 10, 26, 10 };Di2015NewLine    HttpWebRequest wReq = (HttpWebRequest)WebRequest.Create(imageUrl);Di2015NewLine    wReq.AddRange(0, 30);Di2015NewLine    WebResponse wRes = wReq.GetResponse();Di2015NewLine    byte[] buffer = new byte[30];Di2015NewLine    int width = 0;Di2015NewLine    int height = 0;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    using (Stream stream = wRes.GetResponseStream())Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        stream.Read(buffer, 0, 30);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Check for PngDi2015NewLine    // 8 byte - SignatureDi2015NewLine    // 4 byte - Chunk lengthDi2015NewLine    // 4 byte - Chunk type - IDHR (Image Header)Di2015NewLine    // 4 byte - WidthDi2015NewLine    // 4 byte - HeightDi2015NewLine    // Other stuff we don't care aboutDi2015NewLine    if (buffer.Take(8).SequenceEqual(pngSignature))Di2015NewLine    {Di2015NewLine        var idhr = buffer.Skip(12);Di2015NewLine        width = BitConverter.ToInt32(idhr.Skip(4).Take(4).Reverse().ToArray(), 0);Di2015NewLine        height = BitConverter.ToInt32(idhr.Skip(8).Take(4).Reverse().ToArray(), 0);Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine    // Check for JpgDi2015NewLine    //else if (buffer.Take(?).SequenceEqual(jpgSignature))Di2015NewLine    //{Di2015NewLine    //    // Do Jpg stuffDi2015NewLine    //}Di2015NewLine    // Check for GifDi2015NewLine    //else if (etc...Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    Console.WriteLine("Width: " + width);Di2015NewLine    Console.WriteLine("Height: " + height);Di2015NewLine    Console.ReadKey();Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine

4626678Di2015UniqueSeparatorTask<T>
4626678Di2015UniqueSeparatorclass DataManagerDi2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    // The lock on the operation.Di2015NewLine    private readonly object lockObj = new object();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // The state.Di2015NewLine    private State theState = State.None;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // The task to get the state.Di2015NewLine    private Task<DataType> getDataTask;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    public DataType GetDataAsync()Di2015NewLine    {        Di2015NewLine       lock(lockObj)Di2015NewLine       {Di2015NewLine           if (theState == State.Getting)Di2015NewLine               return null;Di2015NewLine           if (theState == State.CompleteDi2015NewLine               return getDataTask.Result;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine           // Set the state to getting.Di2015NewLine           theState = State.Getting;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine           // Start the task.Di2015NewLine           getDataTask = Task.Factory.StartNew(() => {                     Di2015NewLine               // Get the data.Di2015NewLine               DataType result = DataFactory.GetData();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine               // Lock and set the state.Di2015NewLine               lock (lockObj)Di2015NewLine               {Di2015NewLine                   // Set the state.Di2015NewLine                   theState = State.Complete;Di2015NewLine               }Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine               // Return the result.Di2015NewLine               return result;Di2015NewLine           });Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine           // Return null to indicate the operation startedDi2015NewLine           // (is in "getting" state).Di2015NewLine           return null;Di2015NewLine       }Di2015NewLine    }Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
4626678Di2015UniqueSeparatorTask<T>
4626678Di2015UniqueSeparatorGetDataBlocking
4626678Di2015UniqueSeparatorGetData
4626678Di2015UniqueSeparatorpublic DataType GetData()Di2015NewLine{Di2015NewLine    // Get the data async, if the result is non null, thenDi2015NewLine    // return it.Di2015NewLine    DataType result = GetDataAsync();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // If it is non-null, return it.Di2015NewLine    if (result != null) return result;Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // If at this point, the operation has been kicked offDi2015NewLine    // to load the data.  Just wait on the task and return the result then.Di2015NewLine    getDataTask.Wait();Di2015NewLineDi2015NewLine    // Return the async data again, it will just return theDi2015NewLine    // result from the task.Di2015NewLine    return GetDataAsync();Di2015NewLine}Di2015NewLine
